summary: As I'm crying my face off slowly giving up on life I look up and this is what I see... This reflection with these flowers, this...
caption:
As I’m crying my face off slowly giving up on life I look up and this is what I see… This reflection with these flowers, this light. Just art within art. And I just cried so hard and laughed even harder! Damn!! Even at my most miserable I still see the beauty around and what else if not that shows what kind of a person I am. ❤️❤️
